---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Services | Kuma Huang" description="品牌世代健檢、語言轉譯、溝通管道重構、主管世代思維訓練 — Kuma Huang 系統性解碼 MZ 世代">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <p class="page-label">SERVICES</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">解碼服務</h1>
      <p class="page-sub">系統性的世代品牌解碼方案</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-detail">
    <div class="services-inner">

      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-head">
          <span class="service-num">01</span>
          <h2>Brand Audit</h2>
          <p class="service-zh">品牌世代健檢</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <p>全面檢視你的品牌在 MZ 世代眼中的樣子。從視覺、文案、社群到消費者旅程，找出每一個「看不懂」的斷點。</p>
          <div class="service-includes">
            <h4>INCLUDES</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>品牌觸點盤點（官網、社群、廣告、包裝）</li>
              <li>MZ 世代語言校準分析</li>
              <li>競品世代溝通力評比</li>
              <li>完整健檢報告 + 優先改善建議</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-meta">
            <span>DURATION: 2-3 weeks</span>
            <span>FORMAT: Remote + 1 on-site</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-head">
          <span class="service-num">02</span>
          <h2>MZ Translation</h2>
          <p class="service-zh">品牌語言轉譯</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <p>不改變你的品牌核心，但重新翻譯你的品牌語言。讓同樣的價值主張，用 MZ 世代聽得懂的方式說出來。</p>
          <div class="service-includes">
            <h4>INCLUDES</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>品牌故事重寫（MZ 版本）</li>
              <li>核心訊息框架重構</li>
              <li>社群內容語調指南</li>
              <li>內部溝通語言手冊</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-meta">
            <span>DURATION: 4-6 weeks</span>
            <span>FORMAT: Workshop + Deliverables</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-head">
          <span class="service-num">03</span>
          <h2>Channel Strategy</h2>
          <p class="service-zh">溝通管道重構</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <p>MZ 世代不看電視廣告，不讀 EDM。幫你找到對的管道、對的形式、對的頻率，在他們的地盤上說話。</p>
          <div class="service-includes">
            <h4>INCLUDES</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>目標受眾媒體行為分析</li>
              <li>管道組合策略規劃</li>
              <li>內容格式建議（短影音、社群、Podcast）</li>
              <li>3 個月執行路線圖</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-meta">
            <span>DURATION: 3-4 weeks</span>
            <span>FORMAT: Strategy + Roadmap</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-head">
          <span class="service-num">04</span>
          <h2>Executive Coaching</h2>
          <p class="service-zh">主管世代思維訓練</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <p>品牌轉型最大的障礙不是預算，是主管的思維。一對一或小組教練，幫高階主管建立世代同理心。</p>
          <div class="service-includes">
            <h4>INCLUDES</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>MZ 世代文化沉浸工作坊</li>
              <li>世代溝通情境模擬</li>
              <li>月度一對一教練對話</li>
              <li>實戰案例解析</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-meta">
            <span>DURATION: 3-6 months</span>
            <span>FORMAT: 1-on-1 / Group</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="process-inner">
      <p class="section-label">PROCESS</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">合作流程</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <h3>Diagnose</h3>
          <p>30 分鐘免費診斷，了解你的品牌現況與痛點</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <h3>Propose</h3>
          <p>客製化提案，明確目標、時程與投資</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <h3>Execute</h3>
          <p>啟動專案，每週進度回報與校準</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">04</span>
          <h3>Deliver</h3>
          <p>交付成果 + 30 天售後支援</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="cta-band-inner">
      <h2>找到適合你的解碼方案</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">FREE CONSULTATION</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(var(--nav-h) + 6rem) 2rem 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
  }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    background: var(--grad-fire);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: var(--grad-main);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .page-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray-400); }

  .services-detail { padding: 0 2rem; }
  .services-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; }

  .service-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
  }
  .service-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    background: var(--grad-main);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .service-head h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .service-zh { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1rem; }
  .service-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-includes h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .service-includes ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-includes li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .service-includes li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gray-600);
  }
  .service-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .service-meta span {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .process-section {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }
  .process-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; }
  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .step {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--grad-main);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .step p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .step-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 120px;
    background: var(--gray-800);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-band {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }
  .cta-band-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cta-band h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: var(--grad-main);
    color: var(--black);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(168,85,247,0.3);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(168,85,247,0.5);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    background: var(--grad-fire);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; padding: 3rem 0; }
    .process-steps { flex-direction: column; }
    .step-line { width: 60px; height: 1px; margin: 0 2rem; }
    .service-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .cta-band-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
